<div class="features"><a name="features" class="anchor"></a>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="heading">
            <h3>Less work. More workouts.</h3>
        </div>
        <ul>
            <li class="left">
                <span>Thousands of Options</span>
                <h5>One app, thousands of options</h5>
                <p>TapFit credits are redeemable towards thousands of fitness classes; including yoga, pilates, barre, gyms, boxing, and more.</p>
            </li>
